entries.arrived_at_delivery: You have arrived at the drop off location. Stand by for the arrival of our contact.
entries.attack_notify: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 < Enemy fighters detected. >pcontrast3 pcontrast1
entries.attack_stopped: pcontrast1 Tactical Computer:pcontrast3 < Enemy fighters eliminated. >pcontrast3 pcontrast1
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Thanks for the package. I will take it from here. You should go back and talk to our employers.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Ok, beginning transfer now. Everything looks to be in order.
entries.failed_destroyed: You let our contact be destroyed? Do you know how hard it is to find someone willing to work on Naboo?
entries.found_loc_d: Our contact's arrival location has been found. Travel to and wait at that location for him to arrive.
entries.hello_d: So you are the new pilot working for the company. Glad to meet you. Dock with me and let's check out what you have.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the freighter and deliver the package to the contact. Once you have completed this, return to the Yavin station.
entries.quest_location_d: Travel to the location given to your navigation computer.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Wait for the freighter to arrive at the assigned location.
entries.title: Naboo System: Making the Drop
entries.title_d: The Yavin 4 Mining Company's contact has signaled you and sent the location of where you are to meet him. Your prior troubles with the CorSec are sure to draw more involvement so make the drop off quickly.
